              "free_text": [
                "It was assumed that statistical errors of the",
                "amplitude instrumental spectra distributed with Gauss",
                "distribution. Range of cross section variations defines",
                "its errors. The uncertainty is about 30 % (by uniform",
                "distribution), 10-15 % (by Gaussian Distribution) and",
                "8-10 % (by Poisson distribution)"
